: 0px; font-size: 14.0014px;\">眉宇间</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.0014px;\">流露出一股美丽又危险的气息。</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.0014px;\">在第三季中</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.0014px;\">，</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.0014px;\">萧炎还无意间偷看到了女王池中</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">“洗澡”，曼妙的身姿勾的萧炎不想眨眼。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 23px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 30px; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"1.jpg\" src=\"http://www.2349.cn/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190801/1564644480288378.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; font-size: 14.0014px; vertical-align: top;\" title=\"1564644480288378.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 23px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 30px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.0014px;\">美杜莎女王的第</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.0014px;\">二</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.0014px;\">种形态是一种蛇形的魔兽</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.0014px;\">。</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.0014px;\">据原著中描述</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.0014px;\">，</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.0014px;\">蛇人族强者都会把蛇类魔兽的灵魂封印在自己体内</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.0014px;\">，</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.0014px;\">以获得魔兽的力量</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.0014px;\">。</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.0014px;\">想必这就是美杜莎女王体内的魔兽了</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.0014px;\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 23px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 30px; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"2.jpg\" src=\"http://www.2349.cn/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190801/1564644489323413.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; font-size: 14.0014px; vertical-align: top;\" title=\"1564644489323413.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 23px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 30px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.0014px;\">美杜莎女王的第</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.0014px;\">三</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.0014px;\">种形态</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.0014px;\">，</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.0014px;\">就是面前这条可爱的</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.0014px;\">小蛇，它</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.0014px;\">是女王借异火</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.0014px;\">进化</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.0014px;\">而成的</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.0014px;\">上古神兽七彩吞天蟒。因为萧炎炼药师的身份，吞天蟒对其十分依赖，可以说是它，直接影响了女王对萧炎的感情和态度。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 23px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 30px; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"3.jpg\" src=\"http://www.2349.cn/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190801/1564644495695147.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; font-size: 14.0014px; vertical-align: top;\" title=\"1564644495695147.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 23px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 30px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.0014px;\">动画目前还没曝光女王的第四种形态</span>——人类形态</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.0014px;\">，</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.0014px;\">这也是萧炎最爱的形态</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14.0014px;\">。不过按动画目前的发展来看，相信在不久之后的剧情，大家就能看到女王的人类形态了。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 23px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"4.jpg\" src=\"http://www.2349.cn/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190801/1564644504530695.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px solid; font-size: 14.0014px; vertical-align: top;\" title=\"1564644504530695.jpg\"/></p></td>', '2020-03-18 14:11', '来源:高校动漫网');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('188', '突破次元壁！解析《海尔兄弟宇宙大冒险》背后的IP成长路线图', '动漫', 'http://www.gxdmw.com/data/attachment/portal/201907/31/154411qr6srjzz86rhtjj6.jpg.thumb.jpg', '<td id=\"article_content\"><p 250,=\"\" 254);\"=\"\" arial;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" microsoft=\"\" rgb(245,=\"\" simsun,=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体,=\"\">　　6月3日，《海尔兄弟宇宙大冒险》下部（第27-54集）正式开播，首播当天，与海尔兄弟相关的#海尔兄弟#、#海尔兄弟穿衣服了#两个话题便接连登上新浪微博热搜排行榜，分别位列第三、第六位。亿万网民的争相热议见证了《海尔兄弟宇宙大冒险》与海尔兄弟IP热度的再次爆棚。</p><p 250,=\"\" 254);\"=\"\" arial;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" microsoft=\"\" rgb(245,=\"\" simsun,=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体,=\"\">　　<strong>“走心”一如既往，铸就两代人共同的榜样</strong></p><p 250,=\"\" 254);\"=\"\" arial;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" microsoft=\"\" rgb(245,=\"\" simsun,=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体,=\"\">　　针对全新设计的剧情与贯穿其中的创新教育思维，著名亲子教育专家王晶表示：《海尔兄弟宇宙大冒险》的剧情将前沿的科学知识，融入到了趣味的科幻场景之中，通过寓教于乐的方式吸引孩子们的关注，激发他们无限的想象力，这对于帮助孩子建立探究型人格有非常大的意义。</p><p 250,=\"\" 254);\"=\"\" arial;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" microsoft=\"\" rgb(245,=\"\" simsun,=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体,=\"\">　　对于00、10后小观众们来说，《海尔兄弟宇宙大冒险》是一个崭新的故事，而对于他们的80、90后家长来说，海尔兄弟则代表着一段有关科学普及与童年乐趣的回忆。同一IP在亲子之间建立起了一条无障碍沟通的纽带，充满知识的亲子互动体验也随之应运而生。</p><p 250,=\"\" 254);\"=\"\" arial;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" microsoft=\"\" rgb(245,=\"\" simsun,=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体,=\"\">　　<strong>携手海昌，开启跨次元欢乐盛典</strong></p><p 250,=\"\" 254);\"=\"\" arial;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" microsoft=\"\" rgb(245,=\"\" simsun,=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体,=\"\">　　在线下，6月1日，海尔兄弟现身青岛海昌极地海洋公园，为广大岛城小观众献上一份精彩纷呈的儿童节大礼；6月15日，海尔兄弟“空降”成都海昌极地海洋公园，为夏日蓉城带来一场欢乐盛宴；7月6日，在海尔京东自营旗舰店巅峰24小时独家冠名下，海尔兄弟转战江城，在武汉海昌极地海洋公园与广大江城观众热情互动。一连三场“星辰大海”线下见面会，每一场都吸引了数千影迷踊跃参与。两代观众与海尔兄弟一起探寻奇妙的海洋世界，在国民IP影响下消弭代沟，共享童年乐趣。</p><p 250,=\"\" 254);=\"\" arial;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" center;\"=\"\" microsoft=\"\" rgb(245,=\"\" simsun,=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \" text-align:=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体,=\"\"><img data-bd-imgshare-binded=\"1\" src=\"http://news.yule.com.cn/uploadfile/2019/0731/20190731020345334.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 700px;\"/></p><p 250,=\"\" 254);\"=\"\" arial;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" microsoft=\"\" rgb(245,=\"\" simsun,=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体,=\"\">　　<strong>联合快手，再掀全民</strong><strong>COS</strong><strong>热潮</strong></p><p 250,=\"\" 254);\"=\"\" arial;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" microsoft=\"\" rgb(245,=\"\" simsun,=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体,=\"\">　　在线上，继去年海尔兄弟雷欧舞挑战赛走红全网后，今年，海尔兄弟再次选择快手作为短视频独家合作平台，#全民COS海尔兄弟#活动火热上线。6月6日-6月30日活动期间，在@僵小鱼、@一禅小和尚等百万粉丝级别动漫头部大V的参与带动下，海尔兄弟再次掀起了一波全民COS热潮。网友们的各种奇思妙想都被激发了出来，1.5万人次参与者上传了或激萌可爱，或爆笑搞怪的6万余条参赛视频作品，单次视频点赞量高达25万次，总播放量2657.8万次，海尔兄弟贴纸曝光量超过6亿次。最终，以总曝光量7.6亿次的战绩再次印证了海尔兄弟IP的高曝光度与高趣味性，创造了经典IP跨代际渗透、短视频平台襄助经典IP实现二次赋能的又一典型案例。</p><p 250,=\"\" 254);=\"\" arial;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" center;\"=\"\" microsoft=\"\" rgb(245,=\"\" simsun,=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \" text-align:=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体,=\"\"><img data-bd-imgshare-binded=\"1\" src=\"http://news.yule.com.cn/uploadfile/2019/0731/20190731020345352.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 700px;\"/></p><p 250,=\"\" 254);\"=\"\" arial;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" microsoft=\"\" rgb(245,=\"\" simsun,=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体,=\"\">　　<strong>跨界出击，展现</strong><strong>IP</strong><strong>人格魅力</strong></p><p 250,=\"\" 254);\"=\"\" arial;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" microsoft=\"\" rgb(245,=\"\" simsun,=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体,=\"\">　　见面会场场火爆，再掀全民COS热潮，但这个夏天，海尔兄弟比你想象的更加忙碌。进军时尚界，与密扇百戏局推出联名款国潮服饰；化身手游英雄，与《非人学园》展开联动推出专属皮肤。种种跨界举动使人们清晰的感受到，海尔兄弟已经迈上了IP人格化运营之路，影迷们可以在动画之外，通过多种社交平台与海尔兄弟建立多种形式的互动。这种突破次元壁，充分整合线上线下生态资源的模式，使受众对海尔兄弟的好感度进一步加强，也使品牌消费需求晋升为情感需求，进而为IP与品牌的赋能结合提供了坚实的基础。</p><p 250,=\"\" 254);=\"\" arial;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" center;\"=\"\" microsoft=\"\" rgb(245,=\"\" simsun,=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \" text-align:=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体,=\"\"><img data-bd-imgshare-binded=\"1\" src=\"http://news.yule.com.cn/uploadfile/2019/0731/20190731020346801.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 700px;\"/></p><p 250,=\"\" 254);\"=\"\" arial;=\"\" background-color:=\"\" microsoft=\"\" rgb(245,=\"\" simsun,=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: \" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体,=\"\">　　如今的海尔兄弟，已拥有强大的多平台、跨领域渗透力，在线上，通过微博、快手、滴滴等社会化平台进行影响力扩散；在线下，通过整合海尔集团门店的线下流量，以及联合海昌极地海洋公园等合作方为IP增值。可以说，海尔兄弟正在全方位、全流程与用户进行交互，积极布局儿童教育、动漫影视、娱乐营销、图书绘本、主题乐园、衍生周边等全业态，并以此赋能产业链相关的儿童创新教育领域和品牌IP价值。</p></td>', '2020-03-18 14:11', '来源:高校动漫网');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('189', '集结天野喜孝等豪华创作团队！《GIBIATE》动画化决定！', '动漫', 'http://www.gxdmw.com/data/attachment/portal/201907/11/120429fcpam8kuca83uaxo.jpg.thumb.jpg', '<td id=\"article_content\"><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em;\" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\"><font color=\"#34495e\"><b>集结天野喜孝等豪华创作团队！《GIBIATE》动画化决定！</b></font></p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\">集结了<a class=\"tag-tooltip\" data-original-title=\"查看更多关于 天野喜孝 的文章\" data-toggle=\"tooltip\" href=\"https://www.c3acg.com/tag/%e5%a4%a9%e9%87%8e%e5%96%9c%e5%ad%9d\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: all 0.3s ease; background-color: transparent; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(255, 111, 162); padding: 0px 5px;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">天野喜孝</a>、<a class=\"tag-tooltip\" data-original-title=\"查看更多关于 芹泽直树 的文章\" data-toggle=\"tooltip\" href=\"https://www.c3acg.com/tag/%e8%8a%b9%e6%b3%bd%e7%9b%b4%e6%a0%91\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: all 0.3s ease; background-color: transparent; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(255, 111, 162); padding: 0px 5px;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">芹泽直树</a>、<a class=\"tag-tooltip\" data-original-title=\"查看更多关于 古代祐三 的文章\" data-toggle=\"tooltip\" href=\"https://www.c3acg.com/tag/%e5%8f%a4%e4%bb%a3%e7%a5%90%e4%b8%89\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: all 0.3s ease; background-color: transparent; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(255, 111, 162); padding: 0px 5px;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">古代祐三</a>等在日本动漫游戏等文化领域活跃的知名创作者，一起向海外传递“和”文化的「<a class=\"tag-tooltip\" data-original-title=\"查看更多关于 GIBIATE 的文章\" data-toggle=\"tooltip\" href=\"https://www.c3acg.com/tag/gibiate\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: all 0.3s ease; background-color: transparent; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(255, 111, 162); padding: 0px 5px;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">GIBIATE</a> PROJECT」（运营：<a class=\"tag-tooltip\" data-original-title=\"查看更多关于 GIBIATE 的文章\" data-toggle=\"tooltip\" href=\"https://www.c3acg.com/tag/gibiate\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: all 0.3s ease; background-color: transparent; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(255, 111, 162); padding: 0px 5px;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">GIBIATE</a> PROJECT制作委员会），近日宣布作为项目集大成，将推出《GIBIATE》动画版。预计播放时间是2020年夏。并且于今天首爆了宣传PV。</p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\">GIBIATE PROJEC官网：https://gibiate.com/jp/</p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-8925\" height=\"281\" src=\"https://w.photo.c3acg.com//2019/07/118.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; border-style: none; display: block; height: auto; margin: 10px auto;\" width=\"500\"/></p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\">在洛杉矶举行的Anime Expo（2019年7月4日~7月7日）的闭幕式上公布了本作的最新的PV动画，这也是全世界首次公开此作的动画内容。</p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\">GIBIATE PROJECT是2018年10月设立，由日本动漫游戏等文化领域活跃的知名创作者企划，旨在向外界传递日本文化精髓的项目。此次公布的动画版「GIBIATE」是由世界知名游戏画师，绘制了「最终幻想」系列的<a class=\"tag-tooltip\" data-original-title=\"查看更多关于 天野喜孝 的文章\" data-toggle=\"tooltip\" href=\"https://www.c3acg.com/tag/%e5%a4%a9%e9%87%8e%e5%96%9c%e5%ad%9d\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: all 0.3s ease; background-color: transparent; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(255, 111, 162); padding: 0px 5px;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">天野喜孝</a>作为角色人设(原案)，在世界12国同时发售漫画版「生化危机」的漫画家・<a class=\"tag-tooltip\" data-original-title=\"查看更多关于 芹泽直树 的文章\" data-toggle=\"tooltip\" href=\"https://www.c3acg.com/tag/%e8%8a%b9%e6%b3%bd%e7%9b%b4%e6%a0%91\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: all 0.3s ease; background-color: transparent; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(255, 111, 162); padding: 0px 5px;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">芹泽直树</a>进行怪物设定，并且在世界范围内都拥有很高评价的，「伊苏」和「雷莎出击」的音乐创作者<a class=\"tag-tooltip\" data-original-title=\"查看更多关于 古代祐三 的文章\" data-toggle=\"tooltip\" href=\"https://www.c3acg.com/tag/%e5%8f%a4%e4%bb%a3%e7%a5%90%e4%b8%89\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: all 0.3s ease; background-color: transparent; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(255, 111, 162); padding: 0px 5px;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">古代祐三</a>担当动画中配乐。</p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\">在各自领域活跃的“传说级别”的创作者们集结一堂共同创作还属首次。符合全明星作品定位的全明星阵容，面向全球发行的本企划，受到了来自各方面的瞩目和期待。</p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\">■<a class=\"tag-tooltip\" data-original-title=\"查看更多关于 天野喜孝 的文章\" data-toggle=\"tooltip\" href=\"https://www.c3acg.com/tag/%e5%a4%a9%e9%87%8e%e5%96%9c%e5%ad%9d\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: all 0.3s ease; background-color: transparent; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(255, 111, 162); padding: 0px 5px;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">天野喜孝</a>久违10年的新作动画，是否能超过吸血鬼猎人D（※）！？</p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\"><a class=\"tag-tooltip\" data-original-title=\"查看更多关于 天野喜孝 的文章\" data-toggle=\"tooltip\" href=\"https://www.c3acg.com/tag/%e5%a4%a9%e9%87%8e%e5%96%9c%e5%ad%9d\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: all 0.3s ease; background-color: transparent; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(255, 111, 162); padding: 0px 5px;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">天野喜孝</a>作为角色人设参与其中的动画作品，还得追溯到2009年的『森林大帝-勇气能换来未来-』（制作：手冢Production，富士电视台）。动画制作阵容目前还未公开，但是制作人员都是“传说级”的知名人士担当（今后会随时公开情报）。代表日本的顶级创作者和制作人集结一堂，本作可谓是“全明星作品”。</p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\">2016年天野喜孝在Anime Expo的开幕式和闭幕式上作为嘉宾出席，这次在动画PV发表的现场，时隔3年通过映像登场。天野喜孝在欧美的人气非常高，此次发表也让参与Anime Expo的相关人员欣喜不已。作品的概要和Anime Expo现场的情况，可以参考下面的网站中的会场报道。</p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\">（※）以原作・菊地秀行、画师・天野喜孝的科幻小说「吸血鬼猎人\"D\"」为原型的，在2000年放送的同名动画。在海外具有超高人气的，天野喜孝代表作之一。</p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-8926\" height=\"232\" src=\"https://w.photo.c3acg.com//2019/07/218.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; border-style: none; display: block; height: auto; margin: 10px auto;\" width=\"499\"/></p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\">・「GIBIATE」企划官网（日语版）：</p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\">https://gibiate.com/jp/</p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\">・会场报道「Anime Expo全球首次公开动画PV」：</p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\">https://gibiate.com/jp/blog/</p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\">・Anime Expo官网：</p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\">http://www.anime-expo.org/</p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\">动画「GIBIATE」将以此PV作为开始，逐渐推进海外据点的宣传，今年内将在美国召开动画制作发表会。并且也将继续发布和代表日本的著名创作者的合作企划，将会带着国际化视野继续推进这个作品。</p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\">■作品概要</p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\">舞台是2030年的日本。一种病毒在全世界蔓延。</p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\">感染病毒的人会变成怪物，根据年龄、性别、人种不同样子也会发生变化。这种病毒变化多样，因此被称为“怪兽人（像怪兽人一样变化多样）”。</p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\">在那样荒芜的日本出现的一组武士和忍者。</p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\">从江户时代初期穿越过来的这两个人，配合研究治疗怪兽人的博士，共同行动。</p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\">不间断来攻击的大量怪兽人，为了寻找食物而攻击游侠的蛮横无理的人，开始危机四伏的江湖生活・・・。</p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\">■角色・登场人物（一部）／角色人设原案：天野喜孝</p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\">神崎 千水（かんざき せんすい）</p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\">从江户时代初期穿越来的武士。</p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\">在战国时代，以两把日本刀杀敌无数，人送绰号“千人斩”，但现在发誓不再杀人</p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\">「“只用刀背…再也不杀人。我的刀不是用来杀人的」</p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\">「人虽然杀了上千，但怪物还未杀够！ 」</p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-8927\" height=\"274\" src=\"https://w.photo.c3acg.com//2019/07/37.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; border-style: none; display: block; height: auto; margin: 10px auto;\" width=\"500\"/></p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\">凯思林</p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\">吉永博士的年轻女助手。西洋混血，性格积极。</p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\">虽然不善于战斗，用防身的泰瑟枪救了刚刚来到现代的千水们。</p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\">「必须抱有希望，否则是不会长出翅膀来的」</p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\">「觉得恐惧是不够信任，我相信千水…」</p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-8928\" height=\"275\" src=\"https://w.photo.c3acg.com//2019/07/41.png\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; border-style: none; display: block; height: auto; margin: 10px auto;\" width=\"500\"/></p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\">真田 兼六（さなだ　けんろく）</p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 20px; line-height: 1.8; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-family: Titillium, \" typewriter\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" 宋体;=\"\" 微软雅黑,=\"\">和千水一起从江户时代初期穿越来的忍者。</p><p \"helvetica=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" 16px;=\"\" 255);\"=\"\" 255,=\"\" arial,=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" lucida=\"\" neue\",=\"\" rgb(255,=\"\" sans=\"\" sty